0] col-start-1 sm:col-start-auto\">Mais de 15 anos de experiência ao serviço de PME na Suíça francófona. Conselhos comprovados, visão estratégica apurada e profundo domínio do enquadramento legal suíço.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[2rem_18rem_1fr] gap-x-10 lg:gap-x-16 gap-y-2 py-10 sm:py-12 border-t border-black/[0.06] items-start sm:items-center\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] text-champagne font-medium select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\">0<!-- -->2</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl font-light text-navy leading-tight\">Abordagem personalizada</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-muted leading-[1.80] col-start-1 sm:col-start-auto\">Cada cliente é único. Construímos uma relação de confiança duradoura e adaptamos as nossas soluções aos seus desafios específicos, independentemente da dimensão da sua estrutura.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[2rem_18rem_1fr] gap-x-10 lg:gap-x-16 gap-y-2 py-10 sm:py-12 border-t border-black/[0.06] items-start sm:items-center\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] text-champagne font-medium select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\">0<!-- -->3</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl font-light text-navy leading-tight\">Confidencialidade absoluta</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-muted leading-[1.80] col-start-1 sm:col-start-auto\">A discrição está no centro do nosso trabalho. Os seus dados e projetos são tratados com o máximo cuidado e no estrito respeito pela confidencialidade profissional.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-black/[0.06]\"></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-navy relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"navy-grain absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.04]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main py-24 sm:py-32\"><div class=\"flex items-end justify-between pb-10 sm:pb-14 border-b border-white/[0.07]\"><div><span class=\"section-label text-champagne/70\">O que fazemos</span><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-light text-white mt-1 leading-tight\">As nossas áreas<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-champagne\">de expertise</span></h2></div><a class=\"hidden sm:flex items-center gap-2 font-body text-xs text-white/30 hover:text-champagne transition-colors duration-200 shrink-0 ml-8 pb-1\" href=\"/pt/services\">Ver todos os serviços<svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a></div><div><a class=\"group flex items-center justify-between py-7 sm:py-9 border-b border-white/[0.05] hover:border-champagne/25 transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/pt/services/comptabilite-fiscalite\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 sm:gap-12\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.20em] text-white/18 font-medium w-5 shrink-0 select-none group-hover:text-champagne/50 transition-colors duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\">01</span><div><p class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.6rem] font-light text-white group-hover:text-champagne transition-colors duration-300 leading-tight\">Contabilidade &amp; Fiscalidade</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/28 mt-1.5 group-hover:text-white/50 transition-colors duration-300\">Escrituração contabilística, declarações de IVA e otimização fiscal.</p></div></div><div class=\"shrink-0 ml-4\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 group-hover:border-champagne/35 group-hover:text-champagne transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center justify-between py-7 sm:py-9 border-b border-white/[0.05] hover:border-champagne/25 transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/pt/services/ressources-humaines\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 sm:gap-12\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.20em] text-white/18 font-medium w-5 shrink-0 select-none group-hover:text-champagne/50 transition-colors duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\">02</span><div><p class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.6rem] font-light text-white group-hover:text-champagne transition-colors duration-300 leading-tight\">Recursos Humanos</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/28 mt-1.5 group-hover:text-white/50 transition-colors duration-300\">Recibos de vencimento, declarações sociais e consultoria RH.</p></div></div><div class=\"shrink-0 ml-4\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 group-hover:border-champagne/35 group-hover:text-champagne transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center justify-between py-7 sm:py-9 border-b border-white/[0.05] hover:border-champagne/25 transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/pt/services/gestion-administrative\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 sm:gap-12\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.20em] text-white/18 font-medium w-5 shrink-0 select-none group-hover:text-champagne/50 transition-colors duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\">03</span><div><p class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.6rem] font-light text-white group-hover:text-champagne transition-colors duration-300 leading-tight\">Gestão administrativa</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/28 mt-1.5 group-hover:text-white/50 transition-colors duration-300\">Faturação, acompanhamento de devedores/credores e domiciliação.</p></div></div><div class=\"shrink-0 ml-4\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 group-hover:border-champagne/35 group-hover:text-champagne transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center justify-between py-7 sm:py-9 border-b border-white/[0.05] hover:border-champagne/25 transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/pt/services/gestion-immobiliere\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 sm:gap-12\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.20em] text-white/18 font-medium w-5 shrink-0 select-none group-hover:text-champagne/50 transition-colors duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\">04</span><div><p class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.6rem] font-light text-white group-hover:text-champagne transition-colors duration-300 leading-tight\">Gestão Imobiliária</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/28 mt-1.5 group-hover:text-white/50 transition-colors duration-300\">Gestão de arrendamento, acompanhamento financeiro e apoio jurídico.</p></div></div><div class=\"shrink-0 ml-4\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 group-hover:border-champagne/35 group-hover:text-champagne transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></div></div></a></div><div class=\"mt-10 sm:hidden\"><a class=\"btn-outline-dark w-full justify-center\" href=\"/pt/services\">Ver todos os serviços<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-mineral\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 0,80\" fill=\"#46184E\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-28 sm:pb-36\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16 sm:mb-20\"><span class=\"section-label\">Eles confiam em nós</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-navy\">O que dizem<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">os nossos clientes</span></h2></div><figure class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><span class=\"font-display block leading-[0.75] text-gold/[0.13] select-none pointer-events-none -mb-5\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 8rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">“</span><blockquote><p class=\"font-display font-light italic text-xl sm:text-[1.6rem] text-ink/80 leading-[1.62]\">A SRD Partners transformou a nossa abordagem financeira. Graças à sua expertise apurada, otimizámos significativamente a nossa carga fiscal e ganhamos maior visibilidade sobre o nosso desempenho.</p></blockquote><figcaption class=\"mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5\"><div class=\"w-8 h-px bg-gold/45 mb-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy\">Sr. Durand</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted\">Diretor geral, PME industrial</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"flex items-center gap-5 my-14 sm:my-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"flex-1 h-px bg-black/[0.07]\"></div><div class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gold/40\"></div><div class=\"flex-1 h-px bg-black/[0.07]\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16\"><figure class=\"flex flex-col gap-5\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-gold/35\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1zm12 0c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><blockquote><p class=\"font-display font-light italic text-base sm:text-lg text-ink/70 leading-[1.76]\">Uma equipa reativa, disponível e de rigor exemplar. Desde que lhes confiamos a nossa contabilidade, podemos concentrar-nos totalmente no nosso negócio principal.</p></blockquote><figcaption class=\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-5 border-t border-black/[0.07]\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\">ML</div><div><p class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy leading-snug\">Sra. Laurent</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5\">Gerente, empresa de serviços</p></div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"flex flex-col gap-5\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-gold/35\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1zm12 0c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><blockquote><p class=\"font-display font-light italic text-base sm:text-lg text-ink/70 leading-[1.76]\">O acompanhamento na criação da nossa empresa foi irrepreensível. Profissionais pedagógicos e disponíveis, que anteciparam cada etapa com clareza.</p></blockquote><figcaption class=\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-5 border-t border-black/[0.07]\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\">FF</div><div><p class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy leading-snug\">Sr. &amp; Sra. Favre</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5\">Fundadores, start-up tecnológica</p></div></figcaption></figure></div></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-navy\"><div class=\"hidden md:block\" style=\"height:400vh\"><div class=\"sticky top-0 h-screen flex flex-col overflow-hidden z-20\"><div class=\"container-main text-center pt-28 pb-8 shrink-0\"><span class=\"section-label text-gold/70\">A nossa abordagem</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-white mt-2\">Um acompanhamento<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">estruturado</span></h2></div><div class=\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"flex h-full will-change-transform\" style=\"width:400vw;backface-visibility:hidden;-webkit-backface-visibility:hidden\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">01</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Primeiro contacto</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">Dedicamos tempo a compreender a sua situação, objetivos e limitações. Uma primeira reunião sem compromisso permite-lhe expor as suas necessidades e descobrir a nossa abordagem.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Entregáveis</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Diagnóstico inicial</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Proposta personalizada</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Orçamento transparente</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">02</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Análise &amp; Estratégia</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">Os nossos especialistas analisam em profundidade a sua situação financeira, fiscal e administrativa. Definimos juntos a estratégia ideal para atingir os seus objetivos nas melhores condições.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Entregáveis</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Relatório de análise</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Plano de ação detalhado</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Calendário de execução</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">03</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Implementação</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">Executamos o plano de ação com rigor e nos prazos acordados. Beneficia de um acompanhamento regular e de uma comunicação proativa em cada etapa-chave da missão.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Entregáveis</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Dossiers conformes</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Declarações entregues</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Relatórios intercalares</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">04</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Acompanhamento contínuo</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">O nosso compromisso não termina com a missão inicial. Continuamos a ser o seu parceiro diário, disponíveis para responder às suas questões e antecipar as evoluções da sua situação.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Entregáveis</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Monitorização regulatória</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Revisões periódicas</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Consultoria permanente</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"container-main pb-14 mt-14 shrink-0\"><div class=\"flex justify-between mb-8 px-1\"><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/95 opacity-100 translate-y-0\" aria-hidden=\"false\">Primeiro contacto</span><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/0 opacity-0 translate-y-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Análise &amp; Estratégia</span><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/0 opacity-0 translate-y-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Implementação</span><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/0 opacity-0 translate-y-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Acompanhamento contínuo</span></div><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px -translate-y-1/2 bg-white/[0.10]\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 h-px -translate-y-1/2 bg-gold/60 transition-all duration-500 ease-out\" style=\"width:0%\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-11 h-11 text-[13px] bg-primary-500 text-white shadow-[0_0_0_5px_rgba(48,27,74,0.30)]\">01</div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-8 h-8 text-[11px] bg-white/10 text-white/35\">02</div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-8 h-8 text-[11px] bg-white/10 text-white/35\">03</div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-8 h-8 text-[11px] bg-white/10 text-white/35\">04</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"md:hidden relative z-20 container-main pt-28 pb-16\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><span class=\"section-label text-gold/70\">A nossa abordagem</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-white mt-2\">Um acompanhamento<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">estruturado</span></h2></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">01</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Primeiro contacto</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Dedicamos tempo a compreender a sua situação, objetivos e limitações. Uma primeira reunião sem compromisso permite-lhe expor as suas necessidades e descobrir a nossa abordagem.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Entregáveis</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Diagnóstico inicial</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Proposta personalizada</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Orçamento transparente</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">02</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Análise &amp; Estratégia</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Os nossos especialistas analisam em profundidade a sua situação financeira, fiscal e administrativa. Definimos juntos a estratégia ideal para atingir os seus objetivos nas melhores condições.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Entregáveis</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Relatório de análise</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Plano de ação detalhado</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Calendário de execução</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">03</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Implementação</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Executamos o plano de ação com rigor e nos prazos acordados. Beneficia de um acompanhamento regular e de uma comunicação proativa em cada etapa-chave da missão.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Entregáveis</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Dossiers conformes</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Declarações entregues</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Relatórios intercalares</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">04</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Acompanhamento contínuo</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">O nosso compromisso não termina com a missão inicial. Continuamos a ser o seu parceiro diário, disponíveis para responder às suas questões e antecipar as evoluções da sua situação.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Entregáveis</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Monitorização regulatória</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Revisões periódicas</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Consultoria permanente</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-cream py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"container-main\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-premium overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"hidden lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[45fr_55fr]\"><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center bg-primary-50 p-6 xl:p-8 min-h-[480px]\"><div class=\"absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-primary-100 blur-3xl opacity-50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 w-56 h-56 rounded-full bg-accent-50 blur-3xl opacity-60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 w-full aspect-square flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-2xl scale-110\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"p-10 xl:p-14 flex flex-col justify-center\"><span class=\"section-label\">Perguntas frequentes</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-navy mt-2 mb-3\">As suas perguntas,<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">as nossas respostas</span></h2><p class=\"section-subtitle mb-10\">Tudo o que precisa de saber antes de nos confiar o seu dossier.</p><div class=\"divide-y divide-gray-100\"><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"true\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-primary-600\"><span>Quanto custa uma declaração fiscal?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-primary-500 bg-primary-500 text-white rotate-45\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:1fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-100\">Os nossos honorários dependem da complexidade da sua situação fiscal e do tipo de declaração (pessoa singular, empresa, sucessão). Estabelecemos sistematicamente um orçamento transparente antes de qualquer missão. Não hesite em contactar-nos para uma reunião preliminar sem compromisso.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Que documentos devo fornecer?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">A lista varia conforme o seu perfil, mas geralmente inclui: certificados de salário, extratos bancários e de previdência, atestados de seguro, títulos de propriedade e todos os documentos relativos aos seus rendimentos e deduções. Após um primeiro contacto, enviamos-lhe uma lista personalizada e precisa.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Quanto tempo demora o tratamento?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Para uma declaração fiscal standard, conte em média 2 a 4 semanas após a receção de todos os documentos. Os dossiers mais complexos têm um calendário definido antecipadamente. Informamo-lo em cada etapa-chave do tratamento.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Posso marcar uma reunião?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Absolutamente. Propomos reuniões em escritório em Genebra ou Lausana, bem como consultas por videoconferência. A primeira reunião é sem compromisso e permite-lhe expor a sua situação com serenidade. Contacte-nos através do formulário ou por telefone.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>É confidencial?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">A confidencialidade é um princípio fundamental da nossa profissão. Todas as informações que nos confia são protegidas pelo segredo profissional e tratadas com a máxima discrição. Os seus dados nunca são partilhados com terceiros sem o seu consentimento explícito.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:hidden\"><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center bg-primary-50 py-12 px-8\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary-50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 w-52 h-52 flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"260\" height=\"260\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-xl\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"p-7 sm:p-10\"><div class=\"text-center mb-10\"><span class=\"section-label\">Perguntas frequentes</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-navy mt-2 mb-3\">As suas perguntas,<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">as nossas respostas</span></h2><p class=\"section-subtitle mx-auto text-center\">Tudo o que precisa de saber antes de nos confiar o seu dossier.</p></div><div class=\"divide-y divide-gray-100\"><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"true\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-primary-600\"><span>Quanto custa uma declaração fiscal?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-primary-500 bg-primary-500 text-white rotate-45\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:1fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-100\">Os nossos honorários dependem da complexidade da sua situação fiscal e do tipo de declaração (pessoa singular, empresa, sucessão). Estabelecemos sistematicamente um orçamento transparente antes de qualquer missão. Não hesite em contactar-nos para uma reunião preliminar sem compromisso.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Que documentos devo fornecer?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">A lista varia conforme o seu perfil, mas geralmente inclui: certificados de salário, extratos bancários e de previdência, atestados de seguro, títulos de propriedade e todos os documentos relativos aos seus rendimentos e deduções. Após um primeiro contacto, enviamos-lhe uma lista personalizada e precisa.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Quanto tempo demora o tratamento?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Para uma declaração fiscal standard, conte em média 2 a 4 semanas após a receção de todos os documentos. Os dossiers mais complexos têm um calendário definido antecipadamente. Informamo-lo em cada etapa-chave do tratamento.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Posso marcar uma reunião?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Absolutamente. Propomos reuniões em escritório em Genebra ou Lausana, bem como consultas por videoconferência. A primeira reunião é sem compromisso e permite-lhe expor a sua situação com serenidade. Contacte-nos através do formulário ou por telefone.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>É confidencial?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">A confidencialidade é um princípio fundamental da nossa profissão. Todas as informações que nos confia são protegidas pelo segredo profissional e tratadas com a máxima discrição. Os seus dados nunca são partilhados com terceiros sem o seu consentimento explícito.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"contact\" class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-stone\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 1440,80\" fill=\"#F8F9FC\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-28 sm:pb-36\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><span class=\"section-label\">Contacte-nos</span><h2 class=\"section-title\">Vamos falar do seu projeto</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle mx-auto text-center mt-4\">Preencha o formulário abaixo e responderemos dentro de 24 horas úteis.</p><p class=\"font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase text-muted/50 mt-4\">Resposta em 24 horas úteis · Confidencialidade garantida</p></div><form noValidate=\"\" class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-white to-primary-50/25 rounded-2xl border border-primary-100 shadow-premium p-8 sm:p-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-1\"><div><label for=\"name\" class=\"block font-body text-[10.5